templatewizard-close-dialog-body: Leaving the wizard will result in loss of any data that you have added to the template.
templatewizard-desc: A WikiEditor add-on that provides a template-insertion wizard
templatewizard-dismissible-message-close: Close message and do not show again
templatewizard-help-title: Read the TemplateWizard help pages on MediaWiki.org
templatewizard-invalid-values: One or more of your inputs don't match the expected format. Do you wish to edit it?
templatewizard-no-description: No description exists for this template.
templatewizard-no-params-with-td: There are no parameters defined in this template's [$1 TemplateData] documentation. You may insert the template without parameters.
templatewizard-no-params-without-td: No parameters could be determined for this template due to absence of [$1 TemplateData] documentation. You may insert the template without parameters.
templatewizard-no-templatedata: Due to missing [$1 TemplateData], parameters for this template have been auto-generated. Please be aware that they may not be accurate.
templatewizard-remove-template-body: The template you are attempting to remove contains data you have input. Removing the template will also remove the information you have added to the template. This action is not reversible.
templatewizard-search-feedback-message: Recent work was completed to improve template search results. To learn more about the changes or leave feedback, go to the [//meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/WMDE_Technical_Wishes/Finding_and_inserting_templates project's page].
